-
-Release the latest Inspector and SDK updates:
-
-- Add Slack as a built-in host/client template with matching SDK host-template styling.
-- Unify playground client and model selection into a single run picker.
-- Improve OAuth/XAA debugger flows, including stale-token recovery, protected-resource discovery, scorecard subjects, and e2e smoke coverage.
